 &lt;/h2&gt;
 &lt;a data-clipboard-text="https://maxtar.github.io/administration/linux/iptables/#masquerade" class="gdoc-page__anchor clip flex align-center" title=" MASQUERADE" aria-label=" MASQUERADE" href="#masquerade"&gt;
